DEPENDENCIES

- Python-2.7
- libyaml-0-2
- libyaml-0-2-dbg [optional]
- libyaml-dev

TODO

- Implement object linking code

BUILD with CMAKE

In the simplest case, where all dependencies are in default
locations. Do the following in order to build:

# mkdir build
# cd build
# cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=<type> -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<prefix>

where <type> is one of DEBUG or RELEASE.


BUILD with Automake

mkdir build
cd build
../configure --prefix=<prefix> [CFLAGS=... LDFLAGS=...]
make
make install


RPM BUILD

mkdir build
cd build
../configure --prefix=<prefix> [CFLAGS=... LDFLAGS=...]
make rpm7
# After finished, the RPMs will be in rpm7/RPMS/<arch>/ directory.
